All right.

498
00:22:51,333 --> 00:22:53,541
So, you've made a
decision, good for you.

499
00:22:53,625 --> 00:22:54,791
There's no point getting married

500
00:22:54,875 --> 00:22:57,083
until I've become the
man I wanna be, right?

501
00:22:57,166 --> 00:22:58,250
[GOD]
Well, hey.

502
00:22:58,333 --> 00:23:00,333
You're as well-intentioned
as they come.

503
00:23:00,416 --> 00:23:02,166
And you're no coward, either.

504
00:23:02,250 --> 00:23:05,458
Plus, you don't have a big head
about all the powers I gave ya.

505
00:23:05,541 --> 00:23:07,041
[CLERK 12A]
Look, kid.

506
00:23:07,125 --> 00:23:09,250
That might be money somewhere,
but it's no good in this city.

507
00:23:09,333 --> 00:23:12,583
Huh? Sorry sir, but this
is all the cash I have.

508
00:23:12,666 --> 00:23:13,625
[GOD]
What's wrong?!

509
00:23:13,708 --> 00:23:15,041
Is someone in
trouble down there?!

510
00:23:15,125 --> 00:23:18,666
Yeah, sorry I gotta go.
Talk to ya later, okay?

511
00:23:21,375 --> 00:23:22,875
[TOUYA]
S'cuse me.

512
00:23:22,958 --> 00:23:25,166
Would it be okay if I
bought that for him?

513
00:23:25,250 --> 00:23:26,291
[CLERK 12A]
Sure, thanks.

514
00:23:26,375 --> 00:23:28,375
Thanks a million.
That's kind of you.

515
00:23:28,458 --> 00:23:31,416
[TOUYA] Sure, always glad
to help someone in a bind.

516
00:23:31,500 --> 00:23:33,791
That's an interesting
shape for a coin.

517
00:23:33,875 --> 00:23:35,166
[ENDE]
You think?

518
00:23:35,250 --> 00:23:37,083
Honestly, I find the
device in your pocket

519
00:23:37,166 --> 00:23:39,291
to be far more interesting.

520
00:23:42,000 --> 00:23:43,958
My name's Mochizuki Touya.

521
00:23:44,041 --> 00:23:45,125
What's yours?

522
00:23:45,208 --> 00:23:48,625
I'm Ende. A pleasure, Touya.

